	<p>Looks like you have some good ideas. But i think alchemy should be in second for an upgrade. Posions need a long upgrade, i wouldn't say this, but the one you suggested(offensive ones) would be waaay better then posions. Cause a posion is like 5pp for one snare, only on your first hit agaisnt a mob, AND it can be resisited. <br />
But yah, i would like the see the stats buff potions and hp, but the gate type ones would be too much, and you can always find a porter, and if you can't just use gate. The componet free ones seem like a good idea, but enduring breath, i just go to a magician cause im too lazy to fish. They summon EB potions(no componet) and levi rings(i think no componet).</p>
	
	
	
