	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Good points.<br />
<br />
I'll sum up what I'd like to see availiable from Alchemy:<br />
<br />
1.) +HP, +STA, and +AC Potions that stack with EVERYTHING, no alternative statistic penalties. Other stats would not hurt either.<br />
<br />
2.) Reasonable mind potions... higher success rates and longer durations.<br />
<br />
3.) Utility potions that many have to rely on other classes for... such as ports, binding, gating. Invisibility should be an alchemy-crafted potion, so non-invis classes come to us for their supply.<br />
<br />
These would really increase the value of Alchemy. Right now, all of the variations of these have no real value on the market... other class spells can accomplish a superior effect.</p>
	
	
	
