	<p>I'm surprised I haven't seen it mentioned more, but the potion that people ask me for most that I can't make (besides invis) is...<br />
<br />
HoS/FoS in a can!<br />
<br />
This one seems perfectly reasonable to me.  It's something we could cast.  HoS lands on all-level characters, and FoS could be made prohibitively expensive but possible, for those high levels in need/want a little something extra.<br />
<br />
I also think there absolutely, positively needs to be a Shar Vahl gate potion.  This one is probably coming, just slowly.<br />
<br />
The guy at the fan faire in Boston didn't seem too enthused with adding new potions (until Planes of Power, when he said MANY will be added) but seemed very open to decreasing component cost and increasing buyback price.  Maybe we'll catch a break soon...<br />
<br />
Grromp</p>
	
	
	
	
	
