	<p>This is what I'd like to see, Illusion potions!<br />
Maybe something that does an illusion and an effect. Like a potion that gives you haste, atk and regen and turns you into a bear. Another potion that increases your run speed faster than sow (useful for traveling) but wears off like scale of wolf when you attack or cast, and turns you into a wolf. How about a potions that simulates the necro line of hp-&gt;mana convert spells, and turns you into a skeleton. Or a potion that adds a magic dd proc, lifetap or something to melee and turns you into an imp. Or how about a long lasting ultravision/see invis and dark elf form? Only problem with these is that once you zone, you'll lose the illusion and the buff.</p>
	
	
	
