	<!-- message -->
	<p>Im surprised no one has mentioned one thing that I have noticed.  While the DS is a great potion, the haste ones suck.  The DS ones last longer and do more damage the higher level the character is.  The haste ones seem to be at a fixed haste...about the same as alacrity for the higher end one, and a fairly short fixed duration...about 3 minutes.<br />
<br />
Something that would make the haste potions sell would be to make them like the DS potions.   Make the high end one have a level/2+x duration and a haste of level+x.  Considering the cost, why shouldnt a haste potion be almost as good as high-end chanter haste?</p>
	
	
	
	
	
