	<!-- message -->
	<p>A Shaman forage herb ability? Sounds good, but they would have to be careful to limit it in some way - alchemy shouldn't be free of charge, it just shouldn't cost quite as much as it did. Could make a useful AA ability, by level 50 a shaman should know their herbs quite well! Perhaps it should increase with level, and more expensive herbs can be foraged as ability increases - either due to rarity, or the difficulty in harvesting them in a manner that preserves the herbs' usefull properties.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
